03:39.970 --> 03:42.097
Can you get it done?

03:42.139 --> 03:44.683
-Denon?
-Yeah, it's critical.

03:44.725 --> 03:47.102
To your important task?

03:47.144 --> 03:49.146
Yeah.

03:51.732 --> 03:53.108
Perhaps.

03:53.150 --> 03:55.736
