17:52.781 --> 17:54.657
Thomas Tavner?

17:54.699 --> 17:58.244
My name is Laurent.
National Security Director.

17:59.454 --> 18:01.456
I have some questions for you.

18:05.335 --> 18:09.589
Now, Galvanized has been
in this game a long time.

18:09.631 --> 18:12.425
And we're sort of
the new kids on the block

18:12.467 --> 18:15.887
at First Consolidated Systems,
I know.

18:15.929 --> 18:19.307
But don't you, at Denon,

18:19.349 --> 18:22.685
as the world's largest developer
of fuel fields,

18:22.727 --> 18:25.146
want a fresh approach

18:25.188 --> 18:30.026
