to which I am accustomed,

20:26.935 --> 20:29.312
which is through my office.

20:30.480 --> 20:33.024
What is the nature of your job?

20:35.360 --> 20:38.780
I study, investigate
and assess threats

20:38.821 --> 20:41.240
