those two things got confused?

21:04.597 --> 21:07.350
I wouldn't get confused.

21:11.020 --> 21:12.981
Me, either.

21:31.833 --> 21:33.918
My name is Bernice Tavner.
I'm Secretary

21:33.960 --> 21:37.088
