to come home.

34:57.095 --> 34:58.764
Safety

34:58.806 --> 35:02.476
and love, nourishment,

35:02.518 --> 35:04.436
laughter, rest,

35:04.478 --> 35:08.232
and the most important reward...

35:08.273 --> 35:10.400
